    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just that... i've been thinking about it so much. it feels like the most selfless thing i could do is just step aside. to let her go back to her life without a constant sense of dread about my health or my needs. if i wasn't here, she'd be free. it would be a mercy, wouldn't it? to just let it be over quietly so no one has to watch the slow decline anymore?",
